<%=  image_tag "background.png", id: 'background' %>
<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
	<div class="row">

		<div class="col-md-4">
			<%= image_tag "DSC_1134.jpg", width: 300, class: 'profile-img' %>
			<div class="skills">
				<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
					<div class="skill">
						<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
						<div class="progress">
							<div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
							role="progressbar"
							aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilised %>"
							aria-valuemax="100"
							style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilised %>%" >

							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				<% end %>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col-md-8 about-text">
			<p>Hi there,</p>

			<p>I am a confident Rails developer and a passionate Rubyist but I love exploring new languages and frameworks such as Angular, Play and NodeJS.
			In addition to my web development projects I like to venture into Unity game development and as such have a basic understanding of C#.</p>

			<p>Currently I am studying TDD/BDD (Selenium, Capybara and RSpec) as well as automation, continuous integration/deployment and Cloud Computing.
			I am preparing for my AWS-CSA exam which I hope to complete at the end of March 2017.</p>

			<p>I don't see myself as a specialist, but as a facilitator who aspires to further projects by engaging with different people along the way.</p>

			<p>There is a lot I need to learn, but I never stand still and I am eager to discover new technologies and pick up new skills. </p>

			<p>
				<button
					class=" btn btn-primary btn-about hvr-shutter-in-horizontal"
					type="button"
					data-toggle="collapse"
					data-target="#jobHistory"
					aria-expanded="false"
					aria-controler="jobHistory"
				>
					Job History
				</button>
				<button
					class="btn btn-primary btn-about hvr-shutter-in-horizontal"
					type="button"
					data-toggle="collapse"
					data-target="#education"
					aria-expanded="false"
					aria-controler="education"
				>
					Education
				</button>
			</p>

			<p>
				<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
							<%= image_tag "Growth-Capital-Ventures.png", width: '80%' %>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-9">
							2017 - Front-End Developer | Growth Capital Ventures
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				
				
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<%= image_tag 'source-code.png', width: '80%' %> 
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-9">
								2016-Present - Freelance Web Developer
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<%= image_tag 'krater.jpg', width: '80%' %> 
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-9">
								2011-2014 - Creative Director | Krater Leiden
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
				<div class="collapse" id="education">
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<%= image_tag 'Leiden_University_seal.svg.png', width: '80%' %> 
							</div>

							<div class="col-md-9"> 2012-2013 - MA Contemporary Art & World Art Studies | Leiden University
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				
				
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<%= image_tag 'Leiden_University_seal.svg.png', width: '80%' %> 
							</div>

							<div class="col-md-9"> 2008-2011 - BA Art History - Leiden University
							</div>
						
						</div>
					</div>
				
					<div class="card card-block">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<%= image_tag 'logo-eng.jpg', width: '80%' %> 
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-9">
								2008 - Japanese Art & Literature - Universita Ca' Foscari
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>